        <span>
          GPG 密钥指纹：
          <a
            href="https://keys.openpgp.org/vks/v1/by-fingerprint/702F43996B585D7EA231633551AA58935AFE6617"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
            class="link font-mono">51AA 5893 5AFE 6617</a
          >
        </span>
        <br />
        <span>&copy; {year} ShellWen. All rights reserved.</span>
        <br />
        <span
